        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "My confusion is continually before me — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I cannot open my eyes but the tokens of our disgrace present themselves before me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "and the shame of my face hath covered me — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "These things have made me so ashamed, that I do not willingly show my face. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "For the voice of him that reproacheth and blasphemeth — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I can hear nothing but reproachful words against us, and blasphemous words against thee and thy religion, for our sakes; which is intolerable to me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "by reason of the enemy and avenger — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That insolent enemy, whose very countenance is full of disdain and scorn, and threatens further mischief to us, as being the executioner, both of thy vengeance and his own upon us, and who persecutes us with despiteful hatred and great cruelty.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
